NakedSoulsKnit is about tranquility
It¬¥s about being stressless for a moment, focusing on the work of the hand
It¬¥s about creativity, making something real
It¬¥s about coming together, having a small chat
It¬¥s about a good ‚Äùfika‚Äù

Why Naked?
Well, we all are too good at bearing masks‚Ä¶
So, knock it off, no need for this in NakedSoulsKnit, come as you really are!

Why knitting?
It appears that handicraft has an amazing effect on our Psychological comfort and even more when getting together.
It is fun and rewarding so why not create this beautiful plaque you were thinking about or just do some small pies.
If you do not know how to start we will help you out

My name is Anna Jelen and I am also called the time expert. I am a coach, a mentor, a time management entrepreneur, key note speaker and the producer of the ‚ÄûHave a good day‚Äú program (which will be in English summer 2017). Others also call me a Life Strategist.
I can give advice and practical tips and tricks on:
- how to improve your time management
- how to improve your stress management
- how to be happy and live a good life
- good time management exercises
- ideas for your personal development plan / skills
- tipps for your work life balance
- time management for students, adults, kids, actually for everyone - even time management for dummies üòÉ

I keep on saying: we should not just use time management methods, rather live a good time management. Good time management should be a life philosophy, a life style, not just methods and concepts. Time management goes hand in hand with personal development - that‚Äôs what good time management is about.

I will give you hints and advices in a simpel funny weekly vlog for your daily life. Let‚Äôs also talk about: ofttimes, digital detox, how to be productive and efficient, learn to focus and let‚Äôs discuss determination and what that is all about.
Never forget: you need a good stress and time management for your personal development, to have a good life, to have good relationships, for personal growth - simply: to have a good and happy life.
I will give you funny, inspirational and motivational speeches (or vlogs).
Subscribe to my YouTube channel if you like it. That would be great!

Copenhagen Yarn Lovers is a group for knitters, crocheters, spinners and other yarny folk in Copenhagen, Denmark for adults who would like to crochet and/or knit together in friendly company!

We are a very international group of over 200 members and counting, united through our love of yarn, craft and chatting :) All skill levels are welcome, it doesn't matter if you've never picked up a crochet hook/ knitting needle in your life, there will be someone to show you how to get started!

As of June 2016 our meetings are on an ad-hoc basis- you'll be able to see open meetups on this page. We do all sorts of yarny meetups- cafe meets as well as going to yarn festivals in the area, picknits in the summer and even special knitters cinema screenings! See individual meetups for details.
You can also find us on our Facebook group (where we do most of our chatting) and Ravelry!

You can also find us on our Facebook group (where we do most of our chatting) and Ravelry!

My name is Anna Jelen and I am also called the time expert. I am a coach, a mentor, a time management entrepreneur, key note speaker and the producer of the ‚ÄûHave a good day‚Äú program (which will be in English summer 2017). Others also call me a Life Strategist.
I can give advice and practical tips and tricks on:
- how to improve your time management
- how to improve your stress management
- how to be happy and live a good life
- good time management exercises
- ideas for your personal development plan / skills
- tipps for your work life balance
- time management for students, adults, kids, actually for everyone - even time management for dummies üòÉ

I keep on saying: we should not just use time management methods, rather live a good time management. Good time management should be a life philosophy, a life style, not just methods and concepts. Time management goes hand in hand with personal development - that‚Äôs what good time management is about.

I will give you hints and advices in a simpel funny weekly vlog for your daily life. Let‚Äôs also talk about: ofttimes, digital detox, how to be productive and efficient, learn to focus and let‚Äôs discuss determination and what that is all about.
Never forget: you need a good stress and time management for your personal development, to have a good life, to have good relationships, for personal growth - simply: to have a good and happy life.
I will give you funny, inspirational and motivational speeches (or vlogs).
Subscribe to my YouTube channel if you like it. That would be great!

Copenhagen Yarn Lovers is a group for knitters, crocheters, spinners and other yarny folk in Copenhagen, Denmark for adults who would like to crochet and/or knit together in friendly company!

We are a very international group of over 200 members and counting, united through our love of yarn, craft and chatting :) All skill levels are welcome, it doesn't matter if you've never picked up a crochet hook/ knitting needle in your life, there will be someone to show you how to get started!

As of June 2016 our meetings are on an ad-hoc basis- you'll be able to see open meetups on this page. We do all sorts of yarny meetups- cafe meets as well as going to yarn festivals in the area, picknits in the summer and even special knitters cinema screenings! See individual meetups for details.
You can also find us on our Facebook group (where we do most of our chatting) and Ravelry!

Copenhagen Yarn Lovers is a group for knitters, crocheters, spinners and other yarny folk in Copenhagen, Denmark for adults who would like to crochet and/or knit together in friendly company!

We are a very international group of over 200 members and counting, united through our love of yarn, craft and chatting :) All skill levels are welcome, it doesn't matter if you've never picked up a crochet hook/ knitting needle in your life, there will be someone to show you how to get started!

As of June 2016 our meetings are on an ad-hoc basis- you'll be able to see open meetups on this page. We do all sorts of yarny meetups- cafe meets as well as going to yarn festivals in the area, picknits in the summer and even special knitters cinema screenings! See individual meetups for details.
You can also find us on our Facebook group (where we do most of our chatting) and Ravelry!

My name is Anna Jelen and I am also called the time expert. I am a coach, a mentor, a time management entrepreneur, key note speaker and the producer of the ‚ÄûHave a good day‚Äú program (which will be in English summer 2017). Others also call me a Life Strategist.
I can give advice and practical tips and tricks on:
- how to improve your time management
- how to improve your stress management
- how to be happy and live a good life
- good time management exercises
- ideas for your personal development plan / skills
- tipps for your work life balance
- time management for students, adults, kids, actually for everyone - even time management for dummies üòÉ

I keep on saying: we should not just use time management methods, rather live a good time management. Good time management should be a life philosophy, a life style, not just methods and concepts. Time management goes hand in hand with personal development - that‚Äôs what good time management is about.

I will give you hints and advices in a simpel funny weekly vlog for your daily life. Let‚Äôs also talk about: ofttimes, digital detox, how to be productive and efficient, learn to focus and let‚Äôs discuss determination and what that is all about.
Never forget: you need a good stress and time management for your personal development, to have a good life, to have good relationships, for personal growth - simply: to have a good and happy life.
I will give you funny, inspirational and motivational speeches (or vlogs).
Subscribe to my YouTube channel if you like it. That would be great!

My name is Anna Jelen and I am also called the time expert. I am a coach, a mentor, a time management entrepreneur, key note speaker and the producer of the ‚ÄûHave a good day‚Äú program (which will be in English summer 2017). Others also call me a Life Strategist.
I can give advice and practical tips and tricks on:
- how to improve your time management
- how to improve your stress management
- how to be happy and live a good life
- good time management exercises
- ideas for your personal development plan / skills
- tipps for your work life balance
- time management for students, adults, kids, actually for everyone - even time management for dummies üòÉ

I keep on saying: we should not just use time management methods, rather live a good time management. Good time management should be a life philosophy, a life style, not just methods and concepts. Time management goes hand in hand with personal development - that‚Äôs what good time management is about.

I will give you hints and advices in a simpel funny weekly vlog for your daily life. Let‚Äôs also talk about: ofttimes, digital detox, how to be productive and efficient, learn to focus and let‚Äôs discuss determination and what that is all about.
Never forget: you need a good stress and time management for your personal development, to have a good life, to have good relationships, for personal growth - simply: to have a good and happy life.
I will give you funny, inspirational and motivational speeches (or vlogs).
Subscribe to my YouTube channel if you like it. That would be great!

I can give advice and practical tips and tricks on:
- how to improve your time management

- how to be happy and live a good life
- good time management exercises
- ideas for your personal development plan / skills
- tipps for your work life balance
- time management for students, adults, kids, actually for everyone - even time management for dummies üòÉ

I keep on saying: we should not just use time management methods, rather live a good time management. Good time management should be a life philosophy, a life style, not just methods and concepts. Time management goes hand in hand with personal development - that‚Äôs what good time management is about.

I will give you hints and advices in a simpel funny weekly vlog for your daily life. Let‚Äôs also talk about: ofttimes, digital detox, how to be productive and efficient, learn to focus and let‚Äôs discuss determination and what that is all about.
Never forget: you need a good stress and time management for your personal development, to have a good life, to have good relationships, for personal growth - simply: to have a good and happy life.
I will give you funny, inspirational and motivational speeches (or vlogs).
Subscribe to my YouTube channel if you like it. That would be great!

Copenhagen Yarn Lovers is a group for knitters, crocheters, spinners and other yarny folk in Copenhagen, Denmark for adults who would like to crochet and/or knit together in friendly company!

We are a very international group of over 200 members and counting, united through our love of yarn, craft and chatting :) All skill levels are welcome, it doesn't matter if you've never picked up a crochet hook/ knitting needle in your life, there will be someone to show you how to get started!

As of June 2016 our meetings are on an ad-hoc basis- you'll be able to see open meetups on this page. We do all sorts of yarny meetups- cafe meets as well as going to yarn festivals in the area, picknits in the summer and even special knitters cinema screenings! See individual meetups for details.
You can also find us on our Facebook group (where we do most of our chatting) and Ravelry!
